nodes.text: Olivia "Mousy" McCallum (born October 3, 1987) is the daughter of Rick McCallum, producer of the prequel trilogy.
She was nicknamed Script Girl after she was seen on a Hyperspace webcam counting pages of scripts. Mousy played Padawan Bene in Star Wars: Episode III Revenge of the Sith.
